miaowandpurr
============

miaowandpurr is a CAT (Computer assisted translation) tool.

components
----------

* purr - a localization project manager

* miaow - a localization editor

* hiss - a translation memory engine 

* growl - a glossary manager

modules
-------

* vcs - version Control system factory

* kitten - a localization kit factory.

model (data structure)
----------------------

* catus

REMEMBER
========

find -name '*.pyc' |xargs rm

git clone ssh://mospina@git.sv.gnu.org/srv/git/miaow.git
git push --all mospina@git.sv.gnu.org:/srv/git/miaow.git
